o mawala lahat ng aking kapangyarihan

00:17:29.400 --> 00:17:31.030
at mamatay sa matinding paghihirap?

00:17:36.110 --> 00:17:36.750
Sinta.

00:17:37.470 --> 00:17:39.360
Ayoko talagang pumatay ng kahit sino.

00:17:40.940 --> 00:17:41.900
Pangako ko sa iyo,

00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:44.030
maliban na lang kung talagang kinakailangan,

00:17:44.030 --> 00:17:45.400
Hindi ako papatay

00:17:45.400 --> 00:17:47.020
o uminom ng dugo!

00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:48.070
Sinta.

00:17:49.240 --> 00:17:52.700
Gusto ko talagang iligtas ang buhay mo.

00:17:53.070 --> 00:17:54.440
Makakaasa kayo,

00:17:54.830 --> 00:17:57.590
Tutulungan ko ang mga kaluluwang ito na makahanap ng kapayapaan

00:17:57.590 --> 00:17:59.850
at muling pumasok sa siklo ng reinkarnasyon.

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:01.590
Maniwala ka sa akin.

